# ⚠️ 7. Important limitations

Even with BrowserView:

* Some sites block automation (bot detection)
* Memory usage is higher (each view = process)
* You must manage layout manually

---

# 💡 If your goal is Cursor-like browser inside VS Code

You now have 3 real paths:

### ✅ Path A (recommended)

Build a **separate Electron app** with BrowserView

### 🔥 Path B (advanced)

Fork Visual Studio Code and inject BrowserView

### 🧪 Path C (hybrid)

VS Code extension ↔ external Electron browser

